# Design System

Always consult `design-system.md` at the project root before writing or modifying UI code.

## Key Rules

- **Colors**: Use semantic CSS variables only (`bg-background`, `text-foreground`, `border-border`, `text-muted-foreground`, `bg-card`, `bg-muted`). Never use raw hex, rgb, oklch, or Tailwind color scales like `zinc-*`, `blue-*`, `purple-*`.
- **Radius**: `--radius` is `0px`. Never add `rounded-*` classes to cards, tables, badges, or containers.
- **Shadows**: No `shadow-sm`, `shadow-md`, or any box shadows on cards or containers.
- **Gradients**: No `bg-gradient-to-*` on any element.
- **Typography**: Base weight is 200 (extra-light). Use `font-light` (300) or `font-normal` (400) for emphasis. Never use `font-bold` or `font-semibold` on headings — use `font-light` + larger size instead. Use `font-medium` (500) sparingly.
- **Hover states**: Subtle only — `hover:border-foreground/20` or text color shift with `transition-colors duration-200`.
- **Accents**: No purple, indigo, or saturated colors. Use warm neutral grays from the token palette.

## Shared Components — Use These Instead of Raw Classes

Always prefer these components over writing class strings by hand:

- **`<AppLayout>`** (`@/components/layout/app-layout`) — Wraps every authenticated page. Provides the nav bar and page shell. Never duplicate the nav markup in pages.
- **`<StatCard label="..." value="..." href?="..." />`** (`@/components/ui/stat-card`) — Use for any label + value display card. Encodes the design system stat pattern.
- **`<PageHeader title="..." description?="..." size?="default"|"sm" />`** (`@/components/ui/page-header`) — Use for page titles instead of writing `h1` + `p` with raw classes.

## When to Extract a New Component

If the same combination of Tailwind classes appears in 3+ places, extract it into a shared component under `src/components/ui/` or `src/components/layout/`. This keeps future design changes to a single file.

## Quick Reference

```tsx
// Stat card (use the component)
<StatCard label="Active Projects" value="3 in progress" />
<StatCard label="Mailbox" value="View email" href="/mailbox" />

// Page header (use the component)
<PageHeader title="Email Settings" description="Manage your accounts" size="sm" />

// Section header (inline — not yet a component)
<h2 className="text-xs font-normal uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-muted-foreground">Recent Deals</h2>

// Table wrapper
<div className="w-full overflow-hidden border border-border bg-card">

// Icon container
<div className="bg-muted p-2.5 text-muted-foreground">
```
